item.title: Auto Shop Pvt Ltd
item.description: The products sold by Swaraj Mazda in Nepal are most demanded by the institutional sector like hospitals, schools and factories. Our buses and pickups are in high demand. We are the only company to sell small 4WDs in Nepal. Demand for our four wheel drive vehicles has also increased. These vehicles (4WD) are more in demand in areas like Humla, Jumla, Taplejung and other remote areas where other vehicles cannot reach with such ease. Cummins Jakson Diesel Generators authorized dealer for Eastern part of Nepal.
